          <div>
            <p class="faq-q">Are children welcome?</p>
            <p class="faq-a">While we love your little ones, this will be an adults-only celebration.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <span class="faq-number">3</span>
          <div>
            <p class="faq-q">Is parking available?</p>
            <p class="faq-a">Yes, complimentary parking is available on-site at Los Encinos Event Center.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <span class="faq-number">4</span>
          <div>
            <p class="faq-q">What is the RSVP deadline?</p>
            <p class="faq-a">Please RSVP by November 1, 2026 so we can finalize seating and catering.</p>
